summary: This appears to be a court filing from December 16, 2020, opposing a renewed bail motion for Ghislaine Maxwell. The document is an email transmitting the final version of the opposition brief.

events.title: Filing of renewed bail motion opposition
events.description: The final version of the opposition to Ghislaine Maxwell's renewed bail motion was transmitted via email.

keyFacts: A renewed bail motion for Ghislaine Maxwell was filed in December 2020.
The prosecution filed an opposition to this renewed bail motion.
The document shows legal proceedings were active in late 2020 regarding Maxwell's pretrial detention.
